                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">Nr: <gloss target="#t_DA1">DA</gloss> TT 3415</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">Subject: Korean Situation</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">References: C–56777; C–56775;<note n="1" xml:id="d71fn1">Neither
                        printed.</note>
                    <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss>. 931; 250655Z.<note n="2" xml:id="d71fn2"
                        >Greenwich Mean Time was 9 hours behind Korean time and 4 hours ahead of
                        Washington <gloss target="#t_EDT1">EDT</gloss>; thus 6:55 a. m. GMT was 3:55
                        p. m. in Korea and 2:55 a. m. in Washington.</note>
                </p>
